18.description:
Kodkod is not just a restaurant. We are a green business that aims to help improve awareness about our environment, and about our own selves. The restaurant was the first in Chile to gain certification from the Smart Voyager Sustainable Tourism programme. We did this because we seek to offer a service that is coherent with our values as a business, so that our activities contribute to a healthy development of our community and region. We aim to support a balance coexistence with wildlife, educate to improve relationships between us, and with our surroundings, and to participate in the sustainable development of our community.

If you are the organizer of a course and seek a place for it that is safe, natural, inspiring, and together with excelent food and friendly service, why not bring it to our Woodland Pavilion? We would particularly like to promote sautainable tourism, sustainable community development and wildlife conservation, so if your course is along one of these lines, then get in touch right away!
